      "updated": 1776226488219,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The engine implementations of http and grpc are different, \nbut both use sync.Pool for context reuse at the bottom layer, \nand embed the business functions passed by users in the middleware chain",
      "fontSize": 23.878784179687496,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "The engine implementations of http and grpc are different, \nbut both use sync.Pool for context reuse at the bottom layer, \nand embed the business functions passed by users in the middleware chain",
